title: Uncle Si Has a Real Problem with Electricity | Duck Call Room #152
description:
Si Robertson and electricity do NOT get along. He and John-David tell stories about electrocuting themselves. Phil Robertson has an uninvited tenant on his property, and he's eating all the food and not paying rent! Stone and Si laugh at Phil's unconventional use of Febreze. Godwin remembers Missy's attempt to teach Phil to use a cell phone. Stone shares his top duck-calling rule. And the boys give advice on what to do when you make poor choices.
